dc_description_s: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2025. [This dataset is a representation of the PLSS control across Dane County, Wisconsin. About 60% of the PLSS control is made up of the coordinates that were developed as part of the multi-year remonumentation project by Dane County. This work includes finding, restoring and / or replacing US-PLSS section corner monuments and collecting accurate coordinate data. As the project continues the new control will replace the older PLSS control and eventually have updated PLSS control countywide.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
